<span style="font-size: 10px;">Finally, space colonization, though on the distant horizon, is not necessarily a fantasy. Colonization -- pushing humanity's living room beyond its "surly bonds" -- might, depending on how it's implemented, represent a complete answer to the potential disaster of overpopulation and its effects.</span>
